				\begin{document}$$R={R}_{0}{e}^{-{E}_{a}/kT}$$\end{document}R=R0e−Ea/kTwhere R0 is a scaling coefficient and \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
